Revision history for HOP-Stream

0.03    2009-04-05
        - Make is_node() exportable.  This is part of a fix to resolve a
          HOP::Parser failure (rt 37367).  Thanks to RUDY <rlippan [...]
          remotelinux.com> for the fix.
        - Documentation fix (rt 44786).  Thanks to Fany for spotting this.

0.02    2008-06-19
        - Added support for array references (rt 33258).  Thanks to Paolo
          Custodio for the patch.
        - Added 'append' function which allows streams to be appended
          together.

0.01    Date/time
        First version, released on an unsuspecting world.

